    • Method Detail

      • fetchAllAccessTokens

        Map<String,String> fetchAllAccessTokens()
        fetch all page access tokens that belong to the user. a Facebook client with a user access token is used to find all page access tokens the user can manage (needs manage_pages permission)
        Returns:
        map with page id and page access token

      • fetchAccessToken

        fetch the page access token for the pageId.

        Returns:
        the page access token
